<seg id="262">In the SR, the submitted RS are transferred by the tax offices into electronic form and data from the RS are sent to the TD CLO.</seg>
<seg id="263">After subsequent processing of these data in the VIES system, the TD CLO sends to the competent tax offices the so-called lists of errors in the RS submitted by tax entities for the relevant quarter.</seg>
