<seg id="7">On the basis of the statement made by the tenant in the Sublease agreement, the tenant's husband (Mr. Martin Bureš, pers. no.: 760305/3920) expressed his agreement to the conclusion of the Sublease agreement for the apartment before signing the Sublease agreement.</seg>
