<seg id="43">2) International bus transportation of passengers.</seg>
<seg id="44">In the CR, the international bus transportation of passengers is exempt from VAT with the right for VAT deduction.</seg>
<seg id="45">In Germany, the part of transportation that takes place in the German territory is subject to VAT.</seg>
<seg id="46">At EC level, efforts should be undertaken to harmonise the situation, in the sense of article 393 of the Council Directive 2006/112/EC, on the common system of VAT (see 4.2).</seg>
